      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "local_members": null
    },
    {
      "id": "reg:newton_principia::observations__near_earth_surface",
      "label": "observations__near_earth_surface",
      "type": "setting",
      "content": "在地球表面附近，物体到地心的距离   r   近似等于地球半径   R ，   因此引力加速度可视为常数：   g = (G M)/R^2 ≈ 9.8 m ⋅ s^−2",
      "content_hash": "a50828122a0a287b24f4865f0651a08668142c9bf14b5ede46141ed1d0e21b53",
      "parameters": [],
      "metadata": null,
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "local_members": null
    },
    {
      "id": "reg:newton_principia::derivation__inverse_square_force",
      "label": "derivation__inverse_square_force",
      "type": "claim",
      "content": "对于绕中心天体做圆周运动的物体，   所受引力与到天体中心距离   r   的平方成反比。   F ∝ 1/r^2",
      "content_hash": "e2bbda41457071ca57d91a8a1a77f5e656462cc3aaadeaaefad4bfe09fb50392",
      "parameters": [],
