    },
    {
      "id": "reg:newton_principia::derivation__law_of_gravity",
      "label": "derivation__law_of_gravity",
      "type": "claim",
      "content": "万有引力定律：质量为   M   和   m_g   的两个物体之间的引力与两者质量之积成正比，   与距离的平方成反比。   F = (G M m_g)/r^2",
      "content_hash": "46d10d477d1e602273984a590b9a8d62234d97b97577191c8790707357b2ff9c",
      "parameters": [],
      "metadata": null,
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "local_members": null
    },
    {
      "id": "reg:newton_principia::derivation__mass_equivalence",
      "label": "derivation__mass_equivalence",
      "type": "claim",
      "content": "物体的惯性质量   m_i （决定对力的加速响应）   与引力质量   m_g （决定所受引力大小）相等。   m_i = m_g",
      "content_hash": "f2045372cc58ed266de373117a7193e9a777b255c0e044d457641992e24b4bf4",
      "parameters": [],
      "metadata": null,
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "local_members": null
    },
    {
      "id": "reg:newton_principia::derivation__freefall_acceleration_equals_g",
      "label": "derivation__freefall_acceleration_equals_g",
      "type": "claim",
      "content": "在地球表面附近，任何物体的自由落体加速度都等于   g ≈ 9.8   m/s²，与物体质量无关。",
      "content_hash": "cadecb2b18270da2fdd6fd66b1b470083dccfd05a26c5623bb3407b812cb5c1c",
      "parameters": [],
      "metadata": null,
